{"tid":1866863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓捐200萬副口罩後...中國拒給口罩原料","createTime":"2020-02-07T02:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T01:31:14.000Z","uid":15954,"like":84,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0260079acc0d29d01b8000c2003f4f596d23b40a","tid":1866863,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"南韓總統文在寅先前決定捐給中國200萬副口罩、10萬件防護衣和10萬副護目鏡，卻被廠商爆料中方拒絕出口製作口罩的原料，每日口罩產能恐嚴重供不應求，南韓網友因此把文在寅罵爆。<br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》1月30日報導指出，文在寅政府決議對中國捐助200萬副口罩、10萬件防護衣和10萬副護目鏡，文在寅說，病毒不是我們唯一面對的東西，我們應該積極對抗過度的焦慮與模糊的恐懼，而保護人民免於武漢肺炎疫情的不是恐怖和憎恨，而是信任和合作。<br />\n<br />\n南韓《忠清日報》1月31日報導顯示，口罩製造商爆料口罩原料庫存不足，中國禁止出口過濾材料以確保其國內口罩生產，使得南韓口罩廠商面臨停產危機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傻鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4a205223e5c4acb49c487c336b3ededd158fb9","tid":1866863,"uid":88829,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:40:53.000Z","msg":"同支那講人性同愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世上最on9的行為"},{"pid":"e5bb9487ec90b69a3a63b8797060fb5f055009b4","tid":1866863,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:45:09.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f983fd8b1c2aa95eee16ec24b8da2ff172c95b2","tid":1866863,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af4a205223e5c4acb49c487c336b3ededd158fb9","tid":1866863,"uid":88829,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:40:53.000Z","msg":"同支那講人性同愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/ln